				<td colspan="2"><span>Level <b>does</b> affect mana regeration.
<br />

<br />
At level 65, your base mana regen rate becomes 3 while standing and 4 while sitting.  For confirmation, check <a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallfrm8.showMessage?topicID=97.topic">Liq's parsing on tCH.</a>
<br />

<br />
Prior to level 65, I believe it is 1 while standing and 2 while sitting but I don't know the sub-65 regen for certain.</span></td>
