<br />
I have no problem with bard mana regen, we only have a few things that use mana... probably the main one being Fading Memories.
<br />

<br />
The 900 mana, and the limits on Bard mana regen... are the limiting factors on FM...  I think it's a fine balance.
<br />

<br />
Would people rather that Fading Memories was free of mana, with a 30 minute or 1 hour re-use time?
<br />

<br />
As your mana regen grows to the cap, and you get mana regen AAs, and you get more gear (bigger pool), your &quot;re-use time&quot; on FM, and any other songs with mana, goes down.
<br />

<br />
If bards had normal mana regen, the 900 mana on FM would be a joke... and who knows how SoE would &quot;balance&quot; that.
