				<td colspan="2"><span>Pushing for changes to bard mana regen rates will hurt bards far more than it would help.  Without question, they would nerf FM and charm if bards were given caster-like regen abilities.  
<br />

<br />
If you're bummed about not having mana after a rez, get friendly with your clerics and get a divine rez.  Imho bards benefit more than any other class from divine rez.  I also agree that FM is a &quot;get out of jail free card&quot; and shouldn't require constant use.  The only time I opt for the divine rez option is if I die pulling raid content and need to get back out there asap.</span></td>
